description: Gets the current usage information as well as limits for Batch AI resources for given subscription.

subscription_id.description: The subscriptionID for the Azure user.

location.description: The location for which resource usage is queried.

value.description: The list of compute resource usages.

nextlink.description: The URI to fetch the next page of compute resource usage information. Call ListNext() with this to fetch the next page of compute resource usage information.

api_version.description: Specifies the version of API used for this request.
